WEBVTT

00:03:30.012 --> 00:03:32.568
Find truth beyond the way things seem.

00:03:33.010 --> 00:03:34.249
Ask, "Why?"

00:03:34.756 --> 00:03:36.423
Ask, "Is this fair?"

00:03:36.794 --> 00:03:38.969
Ask, "How did we get here?"

00:03:39.488 --> 00:03:41.340
Do this with compassion.

00:03:41.909 --> 00:03:43.683
Do this with forgiveness.

00:03:44.183 --> 00:03:46.271
Learn to forgive others.

00:03:47.031 --> 00:03:50.283
Start by truly learning
how to forgive yourself.

00:03:51.071 --> 00:03:53.315
We are all more than our mistakes.

00:03:54.187 --> 00:03:57.140
We are all more
than who we were yesterday.

00:03:57.550 --> 00:04:00.202
We are all deserving of our dignity.